们以及岛上凶猛野猪的侵害。</p><p>首席制作人坂本博之表示<em>，《如龙：无限财富》</em>的玩家将能够通过第六章开头的支线故事前往栋多科岛。 </p><figure id="attachment_3521891" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3521891" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3521891" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-animal-crossing-style-island-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-animal-crossing-style-island-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-animal-crossing-style-island-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-animal-crossing-style-island-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-animal-crossing-style-island-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-animal-crossing-style-island-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-animal-crossing-style-island-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3521891" class="wp-caption-text"> 《如龙：无限财富》图片来源：世嘉</figcaption></figure><p>“这个功能独立于主要故事，因此你将能够按照自己的节奏进行游戏，”他在接受<em><a href="https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2023/10/25/like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-xbox-partner-preview/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Xbox Wire</a></em>采访时继续说道。</p><p> <em>《如龙：无限财富》</em>将于 2024 年 1 月 26 日推出<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/playstation-4">PlayStation 4</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/playstation-5">PlayStation 5</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-one">Xbox One</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-x">Xbox Series X</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-s">Xbox Series S</a>版本。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，免费射击游戏<a href="htt